# Fork interaction
cast call $CONTRACT "functionSig()" --rpc-url $RPC \
  > thread-03-web3/raw/cast-call.txt
```

**thread-04-mobile** (for iOS targets):
```bash
# Extract IPA
unzip -q $IPA -d thread-04-mobile/raw/ipa-extracted/

# String extraction: API keys, endpoints, secrets
strings thread-04-mobile/raw/ipa-extracted/Payload/*.app/* \
  | grep -E "(api[_-]key|secret|token|password|bearer|Authorization)" \
  > thread-04-mobile/raw/strings-secrets.txt

strings thread-04-mobile/raw/ipa-extracted/Payload/*.app/* \
  | grep -E "https?://[a-zA-Z0-9./-]+" | sort -u \
  > thread-04-mobile/raw/strings-urls.txt

# Check for certificate pinning
rabin2 -i thread-04-mobile/raw/ipa-extracted/Payload/*.app/* 2>/dev/null \
  > thread-04-mobile/raw/imports.txt
grep -i "ssl\|tls\|pinning\|certific" thread-04-mobile/raw/imports.txt \
  > thread-04-mobile/raw/tls-signals.txt

# Info.plist — ATS config, URL schemes, entitlements
plutil -p thread-04-mobile/raw/ipa-extracted/Payload/*.app/Info.plist \
  > thread-04-mobile/raw/infoplist.txt
grep -E "(NSAppTransportSecurity|NSAllowsArbitraryLoads|CFBundleURLSchemes)" \
  thread-04-mobile/raw/infoplist.txt

# Frida detection check
grep -l "frida\|jailbreak\|substrate\|cydia" thread-04-mobile/raw/strings-*.txt
```

### Phase 4: Triage Gate
Every candidate from every thread passes through:

1. **Kill pattern check** (all 6 above)
2. **Evidence chain verification** (location + raw evidence path must exist)
3. **PoC validity** (real assertions, real fork, real app behavior)
4. **Duplicate signal check**
5. **Severity calibration** (realistic impact, not theoretical maximum)

Only candidates that survive all 5 gates enter `triage/confirmed.json`.

